summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5651 for the improvement of The Alley in between Blocks 1 and 2, Holbrook & Clark's Additon, being the alley between California Avenue and 44th Avenue Southwest, from West Alaska Street to West Oregon Street; and certain other alleys, by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 74597, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
